text: Wu Jiaxin is an archer from China. She was born on 28 February 1997. Jiaxin competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics and the 2020 Summer Olympics.Wu JiaxinJiaxin WU == References == Category:Chinese archers Category:Olympians for China Category:Sportspeople from Shanghai Category:Living people Category:1997 births
